data.description: AS-IS!!!!!!! Embrace a serene lifestyle in this 1,198 sqft 1985-built property, nestled in a beautiful, quiet Newport News neighborhood. Meticulously maintained for 40 years, it's move-in ready, needing only cosmetic updates. Roof (12 yrs), wood linoleum flooring, good plumbing/electrical, 1-year-old HVAC, updated windows, and a sunroom. The slightly outdated kitchen is a perfect canvas for your style. With siding in great condition, this is a rare find in a sought-after area. Act fast, it won't last!
